agent-jvm/1.14.9/src/test/kotlin/io_mockk/mockk_agent_jvm/MockkNativeImageSupportTest.kt:12).\\\\n\\\\nI verified with the exact pinned GraalVM distribution after confirming `native-image --version` matched your required `25.0.2 / Oracle GraalVM 25.1.0-dev+10.1`. The issue-specific command passed:\\\\n`GRAALVM_HOME=... JAVA_HOME=... GVM_TCK_NATIVE_IMAGE_MODE=future-defaults-all ./gradlew clean test -Pcoordinates=io.mockk:mockk-agent-jvm:1.14.9 --stacktrace`\\\\n\\\\nNo metadata file changes were needed for this fix.\\\"}}\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_23\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'git status --short'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_23\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/bash -lc 'git status --short'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_24\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed. Preserved work is available here: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fjormundur00%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-7158-fails-native-image-run-io.mockk-mockk-agent-jvm-1.14.9-fc941ae2\\n\\nThis does not look like a `populateArtifactURLs` failure or an obvious missing-metadata/coverage gap. `logs/io.mockk:mockk-agent-jvm:1.14.9/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log` completed successfully and skipped the coordinate because the metadata fields were already present. Run metrics for the failed job are unavailable, but `stats/io.mockk/mockk-agent-jvm/1.14.9/stats.json` still shows the original support run reached 13/13 dynamic-access calls covered.\\n\\nThe strongest failure signal is in `logs/io.mockk:mockk-agent-jvm:1.14.9/metadata-fix/codex.log`: the likely failing stage is the `future-defaults-all