14.9/failure-analysis/codex_failure_analysis_issue_7158.log`, and `logs/io.mockk:mockk-agent-jvm:1.14.9/pr-review/codex_pr_review_6180.log`.\n\n1. Check out the preserved branch and review the test-only changes around `MockkNativeImageSupport.kt` and `MockkNativeImageSupportTest.kt`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew clean test -Pcoordinates=io.mockk:mockk-agent-jvm:1.14.9 --stacktrace` with `GVM_TCK_NATIVE_IMAGE_MODE=future-defaults-all` to confirm the failure mode locally.\n3. If that reproduces, promote the preserved branch changes into a manual fix/PR; no metadata JSON change appears necessary."}}
